{"tid":802841,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冰川會融化？","createTime":"2018-09-01T17:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T20:50:24.000Z","uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"846fad13a7f510089d01c6d5a41b425b0cfeb279","tid":802841,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"前幾日去朋友屋企食飯，佢老竇分享咗個好有趣嘅講法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n        佢提出，冰川之所以融化係因為水多咗&mdash;&gt;降雨多咗/水位高咗，所以先融冰。<br />\n<br />\n        而朋友老竇提出嘅觀點思路如下：<br />\n1）二氧化碳好重，理應大部分沈積喺地面。<br />\n2）即使上到高空，因CO2融於水，理應以降雨形式回到地面。<br />\n<br />\n3）化石燃料產出嘅水遠比CO2多，所以水循環嘅水都會多咗。<br />\n因此推論降雨量多嘅原因，然後再高冰川融化 同 海平面上升嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n       由於樓主對哩方面嘅野唔熟，所以上嚟開po想睇大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n       而為咗方便大家，我google咗少少資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\nCombustion of fossil fuel:<br />\n CH4 + 2O2 &mdash;&gt; CO2 + 2H2O<br />\n<br />\nMolar mass of:<br />\nO2 14.01g/mol<br />\nH2O 18.02g/mol<br />\nCO2 44.01g/mol<br />\n<br />\nSolubility of various gases in water against temperature <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/000440_fadcf38339e9169607f4906a15207277.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F000440_fadcf38339e9169607f4906a15207277.png&h=0a45e199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nComposition of gas in atmosphere<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/002449_461157df069dca98c82fa740df2024cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F002449_461157df069dca98c82fa740df2024cf.png&h=d083b9ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢認為而家嘅用溫室效應嚟解釋，係搵笨（原話）<br />\n一切都係源自於錢，石油市場嘅變動。<br />\n而我亦搵到一篇article講類似嘅野<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.e-education.psu.edu/eme801/node/486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-education.psu.edu%2Feme801%2Fnode%2F486&d=5TLoamFMl8FqW3ZB8ORoLf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4006fc78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.e-education.psu.edu/eme801/node/486</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知全能嘅連登仔會點睇佢嘅講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：真係唔識"},{"pid":"b7709d5d8b30bbe1c0c1bc1448ef01fc9890a500","tid":802841,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b217bd54b6cddaa1eb9e2251af8a318e0d5abae9","tid":802841,"uid":75439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"熱咪融lor屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然實際上點解會熱就複雜好多，但你quote條友真係鳩吹唔使本"},{"pid":"255fffefa9762b9b00589cd6d731e4fa264bca38","tid":802841,"uid":54931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"點樣得出產出既水比co2多？"},{"pid":"4f06185b8fe28cbe7f30f3342c84191cd7641d3d","tid":802841,"uid":75439,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:40:59.000Z","msg":"（1）一年燒化石燃料生產既水佔全個大氣層唔夠千份之一，全球影響唔大<br />\n（2）CO2唔太融落水，如果唔係大氣層點解會有CO2？<br />\n（3）你點解釋遠離水面既高山冰川都融化？<br />\n唔好人地吹到似層層就當真，climate science is a real science"},{"pid":"9b1cae79d1ebbe55ae920675116ceccbfe149c34","tid":802841,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f06185b8fe28cbe7f30f3342c84191cd7641d3d","tid":802841,"uid":75439,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:40:59.000Z","msg":"（1）一年燒化石燃料生產既水佔全個大氣層唔夠千份之一，全球影響唔大<br />\n（2）CO2唔太融落水，如果唔係大氣層點解會有CO2？<br />\n（3）你點解釋遠離水面既高山冰川都融化？<br />\n唔好人地吹到似層層就當真，climate science is a real science"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T19:08:20.000Z","msg":"但係睇返條式個resultant water唔係多過CO2咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"