rap heat 再溶水呢個答案<br />\n<br />\n我已經分唔到真心定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01baaec398d133fc9674ae6788421b6b038a4cf2","tid":802841,"uid":75439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b351384d34690729cfe23ef124b9af42bbcd3a6","tid":802841,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"255fffefa9762b9b00589cd6d731e4fa264bca38","tid":802841,"uid":54931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"點樣得出產出既水比co2多？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T19:13:28.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&gt; CO2 + 2H2O<br />\n佢講嘅就係fossil fuel最多嘅就係H"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T20:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9196d3b1bc5914df1c5a75c6970144552b6b5c44","tid":802841,"uid":23541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T20:32:38.000Z","msg":"講一埋無關聯既野當解釋<br />\n真係得樓主你先信"},{"pid":"f28b5fba1325c44c13a5c5f2f3df16b209c47bdd","tid":802841,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T20:36:00.000Z","msg":"因為佢串"},{"pid":"c37670262f96190960e8425098f982e0b4a184b4","tid":802841,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T20:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同樣係 1 mol 水<br />\n氣體同液體體積已經差好遠<br />\n而且你針住係直接燃燒所產出嘅水黎解釋水位上升<br />\n方向跟本係錯晒"},{"pid":"f5dc3cc0700d261550d82cc5b267230364124b09","tid":802841,"uid":119409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T20:50:24.000Z","msg":"你不如話人體燃燒食物果時夠會產生水份<br />\n所以只要一日有食物燃燒人體水份只會一直增加<br />\n所以人只會餓死唔會渴死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}